AWS EC2 MACHINES:
	ANSIBLE-MASTER: DONE
	ANSIBLE-AGENT1: DONE
	ANSIBLE-AGENT2: DONE

TO CREATE AN AWS EC2:
	Launch an Instance	
	Choose an AMI
	Choose Instance Type
	Configure instance
	Add Storage
	Add Tags:	Important
	Configure Security Group
	Review


